@Rioters 
Please fix the whole.. inconsistent reloading avenue that the client does? Your browsing through the shop, and you all of a sudden see a skin you want. But off the top of the head you want to click off to look at something else -
You have to reload the whole shop right now, just go view that one skin aagain. (Which is why I mostly do skin shopping through champ screen.)
